user_query:
question: On the Wikipedia page for the animal in the provided image, how many revisions from before 2020 had "visual edit" tags?
Attachment: file:///Users/aarjun1/Documents/Arjun/Princeton_Work/newCode/interpreter-translator-rapid_apis_GAIA_Simple/GAIA/2023/test/e14448e9-5243-4b07-86e1-22e657f96bcf.jpg
Attachment File Content:
The image features a puffin, a small seabird known for its colorful beak and distinctive black and white plumage. It is standing on a grassy cliffside, facing slightly to the right. The background shows blurred greenery, suggesting a natural coastal habitat. Puffins are often seen in northern regions and are well adapted to life on the sea, diving for fish and nesting in burrows along rocky shores. 

To find the number of Wikipedia revisions with "visual edit" tags for the puffin page before 2020, one would need to review the page history on Wikipedia itself.

1.panel_description: Identify the Wikipedia page for the puffin using the image description provided.

1.handles: Identifies the Wikipedia page for the puffin.

input_vars.name: query_puffin_wikipedia
input_vars.description: Query to find the Wikipedia page for the puffin seabird.
input_vars.value: Wikipedia page for puffin seabird with colorful beak and black and white plumage.

output_vars.name: puffin_wikipedia_page
output_vars.description: The Wikipedia page for the puffin.

2.panel_description: Access the revision history of the identified Wikipedia page for the puffin.

1.handles: Accesses the revision history of the puffin Wikipedia page.

input_vars.name: puffin_wikipedia_page
input_vars.description: The Wikipedia page for the puffin.

output_vars.name: puffin_revision_history
output_vars.description: The revision history of the puffin Wikipedia page.

3.panel_description: Filter the revisions of the puffin Wikipedia page to include only those made before the year 2020.

1.handles: Filters the revisions of the puffin Wikipedia page to include only those made before 2020.

input_vars.name: puffin_revision_history
input_vars.description: The revision history of the puffin Wikipedia page.

output_vars.name: revisions_before_2020
output_vars.description: Revisions of the puffin Wikipedia page made before 2020.

4.panel_description: Identify which of the filtered revisions from Panel 3 have 'visual edit' tags.

input_vars.name: revisions_before_2020
input_vars.description: Revisions of the puffin Wikipedia page made before 2020.

5.panel_description: Count the number of revisions identified in Panel 4 that have 'visual edit' tags.

1.handles: Counts the number of revisions with 'visual edit' tags.

output_vars.name: visual_edit_count
output_vars.description: The number of revisions with 'visual edit' tags.
